{"tid":2453357,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯又做1哥！成歐洲最可持續發展球隊","createTime":"2021-03-19T11:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T01:04:11.000Z","uid":42246,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0d448df8d423e612bdad3e1372433ca21a11c3d3","tid":2453357,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T11:53:54.000Z","msg":"歐洲權威機構瑞士足球天文台(CIES)發表報告，在「可持續發展球會」榜上，<span class=\"red\">曼聯位居榜首，仲話曼聯未來幾季可以橫掃歐洲，有能力重奪英超甚至歐聯等重大錦標，曼聯再度稱霸不是夢！</span><br />\n足球天文台根據各隊年齡結構、團隊穩定性及球員合約年期進行這次排名，曼聯喺上述3項綜合評分獲得最高分，報告指，曼聯目前嘅年齡結構啱啱好，而且經過幾季合作，球員之間嘅配合亦日漸成熟，最重要係球員都簽下長約，唔會咁容易被其他豪門拆骨，可以專心發展。<br />\n曼聯現時喺聯賽落後曼城14分，今季只能爭亞軍，不過仲有歐霸盃同英足盃兩個捧盃機會，至於重奪聯賽同歐聯就要等來季。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n排喺呢個可持續榜嘅2至4位係皇家蘇斯達、畢爾包同熱刺，近年壟斷英超嘅曼城同利物浦分列5、6位，7至10位球會係修咸頓、巴塞隆拿、馬德里體育會同RB萊比錫。至於近年簽入多名年輕球員嘅皇家馬德里，則未入前10。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GggkoyS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGggkoyS.jpg&h=8a307f42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ea8a3419ef6b36a6f5dd23c9dd0a16191852a8","tid":2453357,"uid":42246,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"皇者曼歸來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a13943d6b14375ee83458a976b5ed71ead894a","tid":2453357,"uid":38189,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"rep